name: Erin Nobody
description:
Meet Erin Nobody, this person doesn't exist. You may think she looks like someone you know, but she isn't. Just the imprecise nature of diffusion. Most images were generated using the legendary A-Zovya Photoreal and Children's Stories models.

Follow me to make sure you see new tools like this, or new styles, poses and Nobodys when I post them. Things move fast on this site, it's easy to miss.

I tried to pour all the cuteness I could into Erin, the results were wild age shifts. I hesitated to post Erin until now that the Age Slider exists so you can lock down her age where ever you like.

If you need a consistent character but don't want a known celebrity, Erin is your gal. Erin prefers to be a teen to young adult (model dependent), have short to medium colorful hair with bangs. She has large, wide-set eyes, cute nose and lips. She's a free spirit so be sure to prompt whatever clothes you want her to wear.

Follow me for more of the Nobody family members.

Click the zNobody tag for more, or the Nobody tag to see other's contributions.

Do you have requests? I've been putting in many more hours lately with this. That's my problem, not yours. But if you'd like to tip me, buy me a beer. Beer encourages me to ignore work and make AI models instead. Tip and make a request. I'll give it a shot if I can. Here at Ko-Fi
